Package: trackROV
Type: Package
Title: Smooth and clear ROV track data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Paulo Corrêa
Maintainer: Paulo Corrêa <correapvf@gmail.com>
Description: This package includes filters to smooth and clear ROV track data,
and possibility GPS data in general. Filters include remove outliers, moving average,
detecte and remove areas where the ROV were stopped, remove points based on a distance thrhold,
and simplify using the Douglas-Peuker Algorithm. The package also provides a plot funtion to
easily visualise the track in a 3D plot.
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
Imports:
    data.table,
    magrittr,
    plotly,
    dplyr,
    sf,
    zoo
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
